s Sikorski|Sikorski]]\n| date = 2020\n| accessdate = 15 April 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Sources==\n*[[Yuri Kholopov]]: ''Russians in England: Dmitri Smirnov, [[Elena Firsova]].'' Article, in: Music From the Former USSR. Issue 2. Moscow: Composer, 1996, pp.&nbsp;255\u2013303 (in Russian); also in \u00abEx oriente...I\u00bb Ten Composers from the former USSR. [[Viktor Suslin]], Dmitry Smirnov, [[Arvo P\u00e4rt]], [[Yury Kasparov]], [[Galina Ustvolskaya]], [[Nikolai Sidelnikov]], [[Elena Firsova]] [[Vladimir Martynov]], [[Andrei Eshpai]], [[Boris Chaikovsky]]. Edited by Valeria Tsenova (studia slavica musicologica, Bd. 25), Verlag Ernst Kuhn \u2013 Berlin. {{ISBN|3-928864-84-X}} pp.&nbsp;207\u2013266 (in English)\n*Gerard McBurney: ''Dmitri Smirnov''. Entry in [[Grove Dictionary of Music]]\n\n==External links==\n{{wikisource author}}\n{{Commons category|Dmitri Smirnov}}\n{{Bibliowiki|D. Smirnov-Sadovsky}}\n* {{DNB portal|121191699}}\n* [http://wikilivres.ru/A_Complete_List_of_Works_(Smirnov) A Complete List of Works] (in Russian)\n* {{Discogs artist|Dmitri Smirnov}}\n* [http://www.lieder.net/lieder/get_settings.html?ComposerId=5774 Dmitri N. Smirnov at Recmusic (the texts of the vocal works)]\n* {{YouTube|user=dmitrinsmirnov|title=Smirnov}}\n* Robert Hugill: [http://www.planethugill.com/2015/08/russian-emigres-from-alissa-firsova.html Russian Emigres from Alissa Firsova ] planethugill.com 14 August 2015\n\n{{Khrennikov's Seven}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Smirnov, Dmitri}}\n[[Category:1948 births]]\n[[Category:2020 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century British composers]]\n[[Category:20th-century British male musicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century classical composers]]\n[[Category:21st-century British composers]]\n[[Category:21st-century British male musicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century classical composers]]\n[[Category:British classical composers]]\n[[Category:British male classical composers]]\n[[Category:British opera composers]]\n[[Category:Deaths from the 2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Male opera composers]]\n[[Category:Moscow Conservatory alumni]]\n[[Category:Naturalised citizens of the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Russian classical composers]]\n[[Category:Russian male classical composers]]\n[[Category:Russian opera composers]]\n[[Category:Soviet emigrants to the United Kingdom]]\n", "name_user": "Grimes2", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eWorks:redundant", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dmitri_Smirnov_(composer)"}
{"title_page": "Malkajgiri (Assembly constituency)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{Infobox Vidhan Sabha constituency\n| name               = [[Malkajgiri]]\n| map                =\n| state              = [[Telangana]]\n| union_territory    = \n| district           = [[Ranga Reddy district|Ranga Reddy]]\n| electorate         = 4,46,678  \n| year               = 2008\n| reserved           = \n| MP                 = [[Anumula Revanth Reddy|Revanth Reddy]]\n| party              = [[Indian National Congress|INC]]\n| mla                = [[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao|Hanumanth Rao Mynampally]]\n| party2              = [[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n}}\n'''Malkajgiri Assembly constituency''' is a constituency of [[Telangana Legislative Assembly]], [[India]]. It is one of 14 constituencies in [[Ranga Reddy district]]. It is part of [[Malkajgiri (Lok Sabha constituency)|Malkajgiri Lok Sabha constituency]]. It is also one of the 24 constituencies of [[Greater Hyderabad Municipal Corporation|GHMC]].\n\n[[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao]] of [[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]] is currently representing the constituency.\n\n==Neighbourhoods under this Constituency ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Neighbourhood\n|-\n| Malkajgiri\n|-\n| Safilguda\n|-\n| Moula Ali\n|-\n| Vinayak nagar division\n|-\n| East Anandbagh division\n|-\n| GOUTHAM NAGAR  division\n|-\n| Neredmet\n|-\n| Sainikpuri\n|-\n| A. S. Rao Nagar\n|-\n| Alwal\n|-\n| Yapral\n|-\n| Macha Bollaram\n|-\n| Venkatapuram\n|}\n==Members of Legislative Assembly==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Duration!!Name of M.L.A!!Party Affiliation\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Indian National Congress/meta/color}}\" |\n| 2009\u201314|| A.Rajender||[[Indian National Congress]]\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Telangana Rashtra Samithi/meta/color}}\" |\n|2014\u20132018||[[Chintala. Kanaka Reddy]]||[[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n|-\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Telangana Rashtra Samithi/meta/color}}\" |\n|2018\u2013Incumbent||[[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao|Hanumanth Rao Mynampally]]||[[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Election results==\n===Telangana Legislative Assembly election, 2018===\n{{Election box begin | title=[[2018 Telangana Legislative Assembly election|Telangana Assembly Elections, 2018]]: Malkajgiri (Assembly constituency)}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Telangana Rashtra Samithi\n| candidate  = [[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao|Hanumanth Rao Mynampally]]<ref>[http://www.indiavotes.com/ac/details/61/42766/266 Malkajgiri 2018 results]</ref>\n| votes      = 1,14,149\n| percentage = 55.4%\n| change     = +21.7\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Bharatiya Janata Party\n| candidate  = [[Naraparaju Ramchander Rao|N. Ramchander Rao]]\n| votes      = 40,451\t\n| percentage = 19.6%\n| change     = \u221212.9\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Telangana Jana Samithi\n| candidate  = [[Dileep Kumar (politician)|Kapilavai Dileep Kumar]]\n| votes      = 34,219\t\n| percentage = 16.6%\n| change     = new\n}}\n{{Election box majority\n| votes      = 73,698\n| percentage = 35.8%\n| change     = +34.6\n}}\n{{Election box turnout\n| votes      = 2,06,108\n| percentage = 48.8%\n| change     = \u22122.9\n}}\n{{Election box hold with party link\n| winner = Telangana Rashtra Samithi\n| swing  =\n}}\n{{Election box end}}\n\n===Telangana Legislative Assembly election, 2014 ===\n{{Election box begin | title=[[2014 Telangana Legislative Assembly election|Telangana Assembly Elections, 2014]]: Malkajgiri  (Assembly constituency)}}<ref>[http://www.indiavotes.com/ac/details/61/34771/239 Malkajgiri 2014 Results]</ref>\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Telangana Rashtra Samithi\n| candidate  =[[C. Kanaka Reddy]]  \n| votes      =77,132\n| percentage = 33.7%\n| change     = \n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Bharatiya Janata Party\n| candidate  = [[Naraparaju Ramchander Rao