he constituency.\n\n==Neighbourhoods under this Constituency ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Neighbourhood\n|-\n| Malkajgiri\n|-\n| Safilguda\n|-\n| Moula Ali\n|-\n| Vinayak nagar division\n|-\n| East Anandbagh division\n|-\n| GOUTHAM NAGAR  division\n|-\n| Neredmet\n|-\n| Sainikpuri\n|-\n| A. S. Rao Nagar\n|-\n| Alwal\n|-\n| Yapral\n|-\n| Macha Bollaram\n|-\n| Venkatapuram\n|-\n}\n==Members of Legislative Assembly==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Duration!!Name of M.L.A!!Party Affiliation\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Indian National Congress/meta/color}}\" |\n| 2009-14|| A.Rajender||[[Indian National Congress]]\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Telangana Rashtra Samithi/meta/color}}\" |\n|2014-2018||[[Chintala. Kanaka Reddy]]||[[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n|-\n|-\n|style=\"background-color: {{Telangana Rashtra Samithi/meta/color}}\" |\n|2018-Incumbent||[[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao|Hanumanth Rao Mynampally]]||[[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Election results==\n===Telangana Legislative Assembly election, 2018===\n{{Election box begin | title=[[2018 Telangana Legislative Assembly election|Telangana Assembly Elections, 2018]]: Malkajgiri (Assembly constituency)}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Telangana Rashtra Samithi\n| candidate  = [[Mynampally Hanmanth Rao|Hanumanth Rao Mynampally]]<ref>[http://www.indiavotes.com/ac/details/61/42766/266 Malkajgiri 2018 results]</ref>\n| votes      = 1,14,149\n| percentage = 55.4%\n| change     = +21.7\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Bharatiya Janata Party\n| candidate  = [[Naraparaju Ramchander Rao|N. Ramchander Rao]]\n| votes      = 40,451\t\n| percentage = 19.6%\n| change     = -12.9\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link\n| party      = Telangana Jana Samithi\n| candidate  = [[Dileep Kumar (politician)|Kapilavai Dileep Kumar]]\n| votes      = 34,219\t\n| percentage = 16.6%\n| change     = new\n}}\n{{Election box majority\n| votes      = 7