 Story''. Simon and Schuster {{ISBN|0-671-24006-4|0-224-01754-3|978-0-671-24006-6}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Bay of Pigs Invasion}}\n* [http://www.life.com/image/first/in-gallery/25102/bay-of-pigs-invasion-and-aftermath Bay of Pigs: Invasion and Aftermath] \u2013 slideshow by ''[[Life magazine]]''\n* {{Internet Archive film clip|id=1961-04-19_Cuba_Invaded|description=\"Cuba Invaded. Foes of Castro Open Offensive, 1961/04/19 (1961)\"}}\n{{coord missing|Cuba}}\n\n{{Cuba topics}}\n{{Cold War}}\n{{Cuban conflicts}}\n{{Armed conflicts involving the United States Armed Forces}}\n{{United States intervention in Latin America}}\n{{John F. Kennedy}}\n{{Fidel Castro}}\n{{US history}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bay Of Pigs Invasion}}\n[[Category:Invasions of Cuba]]\n[[Category:Invasions by the United States]]\n[[Category:1961 in Cuba]]\n[[Category:1961 in the United States]]\n[[Category:Conflicts in 1961]]\n[[Category:April 1961 events]]\n[[Category:Battles involving the United States]]\n[[Category:Battles involving Cuba]]\n[[Category:Cold War history of Cuba]]\n[[Category:Cold War history of the United States]]\n[[Category:Central Intelligence Agency operations]]\n[[Category:CIA activities in the Americas]]\n[[Category:Cuba\u2013United States military relations]]\n[[Category:Aftermath of the Cuban Revolution]]\n[[Category:Fidel Castro]]\n[[Category:Presidency of John F. Kennedy]]\n[[Category:Anti-communism in the United States]]\n[[Category:Imperialism]]\n[[Category:Anti-imperialism in North America]]\n[[Category:1961 in military history]]\n[[Category:Maritime incidents in Cuba]]\n[[Category:Maritime incidents in 1961]]\n[[Category:Proxy wars]]\n[[Category:United States involvement in regime change]]\n", "name_user": "2a02:c7d:198c:8c00:7cb7:f5fd:40b0:dc59", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eTensions with the United States)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bay_of_Pigs_Invasion"}
